# NextGen AI Assistant
2. Short Description
md
Copy
Edit
An intelligent multimodal AI assistant that understands Text, Voice, Images, and Gestures. Built for next-gen interaction.
3. Key Features
md
Copy
Edit
## 🔑 Features
- 💬 Text-based chat with GPT-4
- 🎤 Voice recognition using Whisper
- 📸 Image understanding
- ✋ Gesture control (upcoming)
- 🧠 Smart, fast, and secure
4. Tech Stack
md
Copy
Edit
## ⚙️ Tech Stack
- Python + Flask (Backend)
- ReactJS + Tailwind (Frontend)
- OpenAI GPT, Whisper
- OpenCV, SpeechRecognition
